# 📊 AI-Powered E-Commerce Market Trend & Consumer Sentiment Forecaster
### Project Documentation — Mentor Presentation

---

## 1. Problem Statement

E-commerce businesses struggle to keep up with rapidly changing consumer sentiment, emerging product trends, and brand momentum shifts. Traditional market research is slow, expensive, and lacks real-time granularity.

**This project solves that** by building a fully automated AI pipeline that:
- Ingests live data (news + Google Trends)
- Analyses consumer sentiment in real-time using NLP
- Forecasts 30-day market trends for top e-commerce brands
- Presents everything on a live dashboard with AI-generated insights

